OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy cloud this morning will
OL,6,Fslowly clear, giving blue skies and
OL,7,Fstrong sunshine across much of the
OL,8,Fregion this afternoon. Feeling very
OL,9,Fwarm in the light winds with
OL,10,Ftemperatures in the low to mid 20s
OL,11,FCelsius.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloud will gradually fade to
OL,14,Fgive a fine end to the day with some
OL,15,Flate sunshine. Staying dry overnight
OL,16,Fwith clear skies and light winds, and
OL,17,Fturning cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
