OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FDry with plenty of sunshine on
OL,6,FMonday morning. A little cloud will
OL,7,Fbubble up during the afternoon, but
OL,8,Fstill plenty of sunny spells. Pleasant
OL,9,Fin the sunshine.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FLargely dry over the next few days
OL,13,Fwith variable amounts of cloud and
OL,14,Fsunny spells. A few showers are
OL,15,Fpossible on Wednesday where the cloud
OL,16,Fthickens. Temperatures around average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
